++  +--------+ +----+  ++  +-----+
||  ||  ||  || ||   |  ||  ||
||  ||  ||  || ||   |  ||  ||
||  ||  ++  || |-----+ ||  |---+
||  ||      || ||   |  ||  ||
||  ||      || ||   |  ||  ||
++  ++      ++ +----+  ++  +-----+

Processing Chain

+------------------------------------------+       **complex ice sheets are those
+------------------------------------------+       which are formed of a number of
                                                   smaller 'basic' ice sheets - eg:
                                                   AIS is APIS + EAIS + WAIS
+------------------------------------------+
| read dM/dt data                          |
++-----------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| reconcile into single time-series        |
| per contribution                         |
++-----------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| merge Rignot & Zwally data where         |
| possible                                 |
++-----------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| for each experiment group:               |
++--+-------------------------------------^+
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | for each basic* ice sheet:         | |
 | ++--+-------------------------------^+ |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | compute average dM/dt of     | |  |
 |  | | sheet data from this group   | |  |
 |  | ++-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | compute dM series from dM/dt | |  |
 |  | ++-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | store avg. dM/dt and dM      +-+  |
 |  | +------------------------------+    |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | for each complex** ice sheet:      | |
 | ++--+-------------------------------^+ |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | calc. sum of group average   | |  |
 |  | | dM/dt series for constituent | |  |
 |  | | ice sheets                   | |  |
 |  | ++-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | compute dM series from dM/dt | |  |
 |  | ++-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  |  |                               |  |
 |  | +v-----------------------------+ |  |
 |  | | store avg. dM/dt and dM      +-+  |
 |  | +------------------------------+    |
 |  +-------------------------------------+
+v-----------------------------------------+
| for each basic* ice sheet:               |
++--+-------------------------------------^+
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | calc. cross|group avg. dM/dt       | |
 | ++-----------------------------------+ |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | calc. dM series from dM/dt         | |
 | ++-----------------------------------+ |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | store avg. dM/dt and dM            +-+
 | +------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| for each complex** ice sheet:            |
++--+-------------------------------------^+
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | calc. sum of cross-group avg.      | |
 | | dM/dt series from constituent      | |
 | | ice sheets                         | |
 | ++-----------------------------------+ |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | calc. dM series from dM/dt         | |
 | ++-----------------------------------+ |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | store avg. dM/dt and dM            +-+
 | +------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| for each group:                          |
++--+-------------------------------------^+
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | plot group dM/dt intra|comparison  | |
 | ++-----------------------------------+ |
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | plot group dM intra|comparison     +-+
 | +------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| plot cross|group dM/dt inter|comparison  |
++-----------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| plot cross|group dM inter|comparison     |
++-----------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| for each complex** region:               |
++--+-------------------------------------^+
 |  |                                     |
 | +v-----------------------------------+ |
 | | plot comparison of cross-group dM  | |
 | | from constituent ice sheets        +-+
 | +------------------------------------+
 |
+v-----------------------------------------+
| finish                                   |
+------------------------------------------+
